    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>At DesignHammer, we've used the <a href="https://drupal.org/project/migrate">Migrate module</a> on many projects, with a variety of use cases: Drupal-to-Drupal migrations; importing content from CSVs or XML to populate a new site build; importing XML from an eBook as nodes for an online version of the book content, and so on. It's a flexible, stable module that provides a great API for getting content from point A to point B.</p></div></div></div>
